1. *Leži* u hladu i uživa u miru. (She is lying in the shade and enjoying the peace.)
2. Ona je *ležala* u travi i zaspala. (She was lying in the grass and fell asleep.)
3. *Leži* bez pokreta. (It lies motionless.)
4. Njegovi ostaci *leže* u grobu. (His remains are lying in the grave.)
5. Ona je *ležala* na kauču i čitala knjigu. (She was lying on the couch and reading a book.)
6. *Leži* mirno! (Lie still!)